---
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<div class="projects">
  <h2 class="projects__heading">Projects</h2>
  <p>
    On my programming journey, I have created a few projects — as part of the
    Udemy courses that I am undertaking and as my own pet projects — which I am
    happy to share with you on this website. In fact, this website is also a
    project of mine!
  </p>

  <Card />
  <Card />
  <Card />
</div>

<style>
  .projects {
    display: flex;
    background-color: #f1f3f5;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 48px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .projects__heading {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: Merriweather;
    margin-top: 64px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    font-size: 44px;
  }

  .projects p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 2;
    margin: 0 30px;
  }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
    .projects__heading {
      font-size: 30px;
      letter-spacing: -0.8px;
    }
  }
</style>
